Package: MLM
Type: Package
Title: Estimate Cell-type Proportions of Bulk RNA-Seq Data with Linear Mixed Model
Version: 0.1.0
Author: LiyangSong
Maintainer: LiyangSong <songliyang@westlake.edu.cn>
Description: Package implementing the mixed linear model (MLM) to estimate cell-type proportions in 
		bulk gene expression data.It is based on reference gene expression from single-cell RNA-Seq data. 
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
biocViews: limma, Seurat
